   europe    king aistulf of the lombards again threaten rome with a view to making it his capital , but the franks under pepin iii ( " the short " ) arrives with his sons charles and carloman , defeats aistulf , and confers the donation of pepin which establishes the papal states ( including lands of ravenna and the pentapolis ) .

european history : these states that included rome were established in 756 & were absorbed by italy in 1870

